### Tarballs

pepper is distributed as a source code package. You
can grab the latest release from the [file list at
SourceForge](http://sourceforge.net/projects/scm-pepper/files/) or use
these direct links:

* [pepper-0.2.4.tar.gz](http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/scm-pepper/pepper-0.2.4.tar.gz)
* [pepper-0.2.4.tar.bz2](http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/scm-pepper/pepper-0.2.4.tar.bz2)

Previous releases are available at
[SourceForge](http://sourceforge.net/projects/scm-pepper/files/). The plain-text
[change log](ChangeLog) summarizes the changes between subsequent releases.

Please see the [[Documentation]] page for installation instructions and
basic usage information.


